Class PatternMatcherFind

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.codeteapot.jmibeans.testing.session.sentence.PatternMatcherFind

  • public class PatternMatcherFind
extends Object
    Find operation of a regular expression matcher.

    Matches if the find operation matches, and so do any group operations it has.

    See Also:
